</taxonomicName>
, by subsequent designation of 
<bibRefCitation author="Curtis" box="[1026,1248,1446,1468]" pageId="19" pageNumber="518" refString="Curtis, J. (1835) British entomology; being illustrations and descriptions of the genera of insects found in Great Britain and Ireland. Vol. 12. J. Curtis, London, pls. 530 - 577." type="book chapter" year="1835">Curtis (1835: pl. 531)</bibRefCitation>
